Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deleteAllPtnFeedthroughs(25.10)                deleteAllPtnFeedthroughs(25.10)

Name
       deleteAllPtnFeedthroughs  -  Deletes  all the partition feedthrough ob-
       jects in the floorplan

Syntax
       deleteAllPtnFeedthroughs

       [-help]

       Deletes all the partition feedthrough objects in the floorplan. You can
       use this command during partition floorplanning.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description of the deleteAllPtnFeedthroughs com-
              mand.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man deleteAllPtnFeedthroughs

Example
       The following command removes all feedthrough objects from  the  floor-
       plan:

       deleteAllPtnFeedthroughs

Related Information
              * Partitioning the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

              * Inserting Feedthroughs

